{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, there were main effects of input (F(1, 196) = 9.45; P = 0.002) and time (F(4.55, 892.35) = 14.80; P < 0.001).",
    "No other effects were significant (all P values > 0.06).",
    "Thus, as illustrated in Fig. 1f, both the AI's input and its label contributed to enhanced bias in humans over time.",
    "Finally, we assessed the rate of decision changes among participants.",
    "Participants were more likely to change their classification when their associate disagreed with them."
  ]
}